name: Tribal Edition - DAYAK (Place of Origin Kalimantan)
description:
in this culture series will show some artwork about the tribes and cultures that exist in Indonesia.

Indonesia is known for its diverse ethnic groups, cultures, and customs. With so many tribes and cultures, Indonesia is dubbed as a multicultural country. One of the tribes in Indonesia is the Dayak tribe from the island of Borneo or Kalimantan.
